**Story**
Once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree, which was on the bank of a river. In the same forest, there lived a crocodile and his wife
One day the Crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree. The kind hearted Monkey offered him some fruits and the Crocodile came back the next day for more fruits
As he loved them. As days passed by, the Crocodile and the Monkey became bast friends